338
00:22:36,888 --> 00:22:38,623
And why would they want to do that?

339
00:22:38,623 --> 00:22:42,727
Well, you know,
I think-- l- we- we think...

340
00:22:42,727 --> 00:22:46,397
that... there- there may have been
an accident a while back.

341
00:22:46,397 --> 00:22:48,199
And- and- and we think that
the other driver,

342
00:22:48,199 --> 00:22:49,467
that he might be trying to hurt us.

