381
00:25:01,733 --> 00:25:02,700
That's hilarious.

382
00:25:02,700 --> 00:25:05,303
You're- you're- you're just a real riot.

383
00:25:05,303 --> 00:25:06,838
Well, you used to think so.

384
00:25:06,838 --> 00:25:08,539
Well I came to my senses.

385
00:25:08,539 --> 00:25:11,167
So if you're here to insult me,
just leave.

386
00:25:16,180 --> 00:25:18,273
Shelley's stuck in a ditch.

387
00:25:19,350 --> 00:25:20,018
What?

388
00:25:20,018 --> 00:25:22,086
I heard it on my scanner.

389
00:25:22,086 --> 00:25:23,421
Well how do you know it's her?

390
00:25:23,421 --> 00:25:25,089
Boyfriend's name is Ryan, right?

391
00:25:25,089 --> 00:25:27,291
Oh, that jerk. Don't remind me.

392
00:25:27,291 --> 00:25:29,761
Yeah.
