in an accident.

395
00:25:32,997 --> 00:25:34,432
Uh, with somebody else, I mean.

396
00:25:34,432 --> 00:25:35,466
Well, is she okay?

397
00:25:35,466 --> 00:25:36,567
I didn't hear anything about
any injuries.

398
00:25:36,567 --> 00:25:39,058
All I heard was that
they're stuck in a ditch.

399
00:25:39,637 --> 00:25:41,806
Well, go pull her out.

400
00:25:41,806 --> 00:25:44,609
N- you know, the sheriff's on it.

401
00:25:44,609 --> 00:25:46,144
I- l- l- I was on my way home.

402
00:25:46,144 --> 00:25:47,745
I just thought maybe you'd like to know.

403
00:25:47,745 --> 00:25:49,781
Well, Larry, why can't
you just go pull her out?

404
00:25:49,781 --> 00:25:53,451
Because. I've been working
since seven o'clock this morning.

405
00:25:53,451 --> 00:25:54,719
I'm exhausted.

406
00:25:54,719 --> 00:25:56,120
I'm going to go home and
get a little bit of shut eye.

407
00:25:56,120 --> 00:25:57,955
Oh, on a night like this?
Bull.

408
00:25:57,955 --> 00:25:59,057
You're not going to go to sleep.

409
00:25:59,057 --> 00:26:01,218
There's too much business out there.

410
00:26:02,693 --> 00:26:03,528
You know, sheriff's on it.

411
00:26:03,528 --> 00:26:04,829
I'm- I'm on my way home.

412
00:26:04,829 --> 00:26:06,564
I just thought you might want to know.

413
00:26:06,564 --> 00:26:09,700
You're going to leave my daughter stuck in
a ditch to get back at me?

414
00:26:09,700 --> 00:26:11,936
Oh, since when do you care
about your daughter?

415
00:26:11,936 --> 00:26:14,338
Since when do you care about anybody?

416
00:26:14,338 --> 00:26:16,636
I care about a lot of people.

417
00:26:17,809 --> 00:26:20,710
Fact, there's just one person
I don't care about.

418
00:26:26,484 --> 00:26:27,815
Always a pleasure, Gayle.

419
00:26:46,037 --> 00:26:47,629
Some tow truck driver.

420
00:26:57,181 --> 00:27:04,747
Dear God, please keep Shelley safe.
Please.

421
00:27:32,817 --> 00:27:34,341
Not without protection.

422
00:27:41,759 --> 00:27:44,626
I don't want to get pregnant,
stuck in this town forever.

423
00:28:06,317 --> 00:28:07,852
Are you sure you got
the location correct?

424
00:28:07,852 --> 00:28:09,520
Because I've been up and down Montpelier
