425
00:28:09,520 --> 00:28:11,756
I'm not seeing any stranded white jeep.

426
00:28:11,756 --> 00:28:13,124
You want to get some more guys on this?

427
00:28:13,124 --> 00:28:14,853
Yeah, I think we better, yeah.

428
00:28:26,837 --> 00:28:28,236
Want to hit this?

429
00:28:29,640 --> 00:28:31,369
Don't mind if I do.
Yeah.

430
00:28:34,078 --> 00:28:35,739
It's kind of weird that
he hasn't come home yet.

