443
00:29:26,931 --> 00:29:28,733
Nine-one-one emergency.

444
00:29:28,733 --> 00:29:30,034
Hey, yeah.

445
00:29:30,034 --> 00:29:35,006
This is, uh, this is Ryan Dunbar,
